        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1961045881" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4325564876590409985"><i>Seriously?!</i> Christ this is a mess. I&apos;m obviously wrong considering all the glowing praise and award-winning going on here, but can&apos;t for the life of me understand what the fuss is about. I mean, great concept but poor execution. Way too many of the chapters felt off or forced, I didn&apos;t invest in any of the characters, and the ending didn&apos;t redeem it - in fact, probably made it worse.<br/><br/>Very disappointed.</span>
  <span id="freeText4325564876590409985" style="display:none"><i>Seriously?!</i> Christ this is a mess. I'm obviously wrong considering all the glowing praise and award-winning going on here, but can't for the life of me understand what the fuss is about. I mean, great concept but poor execution. Way too many of the chapters felt off or forced, I didn't invest in any of the characters, and the ending didn't redeem it - in fact, probably made it worse.<br /><br />Very disappointed.</span>
